{"tid":2361324,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"適合先係埋一齊，定係一齊左先睇適唔適合？","createTime":"2021-01-10T14:11:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T15:27:53.000Z","uid":184220,"like":5,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"198606b5baae04adbbd28d9cd197136c7a9a0da2","tid":2361324,"uid":184220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T14:11:46.000Z","msg":"一直曖昧，明知大家有好感，卻怕到頭來並唔係真係中意而唔開始呢段關係，不斷觀察，確保互相適合再一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有好感後直接一齊，男女朋友關係下比起曖昧相處可以更直接，但有機會因相處後不滿對方，繼而不和，分手機會較大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講白啲就係其中一方想一齊，唔想拖住，而另一方就怕最後唔適合，所以唔想一齊住，維持曖昧關係一段時間再決定。"},{"pid":"886c6215990e3526ad86e5ec44e23206595cc24b","tid":2361324,"uid":873,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T14:31:24.000Z","msg":"蔣麗芸 多謝"},{"pid":"6fbdbfd4e1b5955dd34ef7cac94a3490d53fc865","tid":2361324,"uid":271223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T15:03:19.000Z","msg":"理性做法係前者，但係有時好難控制<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3cba5a8ab63fbac3c7c4ac1498425d23cd24c96","tid":2361324,"uid":137847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T15:09:47.000Z","msg":"一齊左先睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a90105e94aee3ad3c4b91c40e481a9b55e3d093","tid":2361324,"uid":186374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T15:14:38.000Z","msg":"雖然一齊都未必可以好快見到，但唔一齊就一定唔會知真面目"},{"pid":"9c0fedfacf334032a74ae9fff247b811198e56d2","tid":2361324,"uid":107656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T15:16:38.000Z","msg":"試咗車先啦"},{"pid":"ba3aa39e8eef8b642d717359896726d3ea2ad0be","tid":2361324,"uid":18612,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"198606b5baae04adbbd28d9cd197136c7a9a0da2","tid":2361324,"uid":184220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T14:11:46.000Z","msg":"